    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK451">
<l>ciṟṟiṉa mañcum perumai ciṟumaitāṉ</l>
<l>cuṟṟamāc cūḻntu viṭum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>(True) greatness fears the society of the base it is only the low - minded who will regard them as friends.</l>
            </lg>
